{"type":"message","id":"d6ab97a5","parentId":"5bb61055","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:43:19.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户是 AI 算法研究员，需要我帮忙收集具身智能的权威资料并整理算法调研报告。这是一个需要网络搜索的任务，我需要：\n\n1. 搜索具身智能的权威资料、综述论文、基准数据集等\n2. 整理成一份结构化的调研报告\n\n让我先进行几个关键搜索：\n- 具身智能 综述/overview\n- Embodied AI survey 2025 2026\n- 具身智能 benchmark dataset\n- 具身智能 VLA 模型\n\n我会用 web_search 来收集信息。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_8b03ba3406dc457ba7159771","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"具身智能 Embodied AI 综述 survey 2025 2026","count":10,"language":"en"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_fbaa21be259d48cb82d516cc","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Embodied AI benchmark dataset VLA model robotics learning","count":10,"language":"en"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_04af00636b214bca8d069297","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"具身智能 视觉语言动作模型 VLA RT-1 RT-2 OpenVLA","count":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":1551,"output":307,"cacheRead":10377,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12235,"cost":{"input":0.00017061000000000002,"output":0.00008596000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00025657}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774237394671}}
