{"type":"message","id":"b4b6d17d","parentId":"523bc2cf","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:58:58.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提到可以用\"目录下的多模搜索引擎\"搜索。根据我之前看到的 available_skills，有一个 `multi-search-engine` skill：\n\n```\n<skill>\n  <name>multi-search-engine</name>\n  <description>Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.</description>\n  <location>~/.openclaw/workspace-fox-embodied_ai/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md</location>\n</skill>\n```\n\n这个 skill 在用户的工作目录下，不需要 API key，支持国内和全球搜索引擎。让我先读取这个 skill 的 SKILL.md 文件，了解如何使用它。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！我可以用工作目录下的多模搜索引擎。让我先看一下这个技能的使用方法：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e04223654cb3451b8b50244b","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-embodied_ai/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":18016,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":10377,"totalTokens":28633,"cost":{"input":0.00198176,"output":0.00006720000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00204896}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774241932291}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf7659ba","parentId":"b4b6d17d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:58:58.977Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e04223654cb3451b8b50244b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774241938971}}
{"type":"message","id":"934b1212","parentId":"bf7659ba","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:59:05.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个 multi-search-engine skill 使用 web_fetch 工具直接抓取搜索引擎的结果页面，不需要 API key。我可以用 Google、Bing、Baidu 等搜索引擎来搜索具身智能的相关信息。\n\n让我用多个搜索引擎搜索具身智能的资料：\n1. Google 搜索 Embodied AI survey/review\n2. Bing 搜索具身智能\n3. 可能再用 Google 搜索 VLA 模型、数据集等\n\n我会用 web_fetch 工具抓取搜索结果页面，然后整理信息。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！这个多模搜索引擎不需要 API key，直接用 `web_fetch` 抓取搜索结果页面。我来帮你搜索具身智能的权威资料：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4a0397af6ef14e5bb4dab9e9","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":8000,"url":"https://www.google.com/search?q=Embodied+AI+survey+2025+comprehensive+review+robotics+VLA"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_88abd972357246e1939f7d35","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":8000,"url":"https://www.google.com/search?q=Embodied+AI+benchmark+dataset+Habitat+AI2-THOR+Open+X-Embodiment"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_407a590d63344d9094aee6d4","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":8000,"url":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=具身智能+VLA+RT-2+OpenVLA+机器人学习"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":19305,"output":387,"cacheRead":10377,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30069,"cost":{"input":0.00212355,"output":0.00010836000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00223191}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774241938978}}
